videos.description:
Front Roll (High Rings)

1) Start and finish in full support
2) Lean forward through dip to initiate roll
3) Body in tuck position through roll
4) Pull and turn over must be in sync
5) As shoulders rise, lower body directs toward ground
6) Rings/hands stay close to hips through rolling action

videos.title:
MONKEY METHOD
STRICT PULL UPS
videos.description:
STRICT PULL UPS: 
1)dead hang to start (head neutral, eyes 
forward, elbows locked out, legs and feet 
together, no angle at shoulder)
2)initiate pull from lats
3)keep body hollow throughout
 pull.
4)eyes stay fixed on same point on 
horizon throughout
5)point A to point B in as much of 
a straight line as possible. 
6)pull as high as possible with each rep.  
Not just to chin over bar.
7)keep position in place on descent        www.pwrmnky.com

repetition
